xfrm interface: fix oops when deleting a x-netns interface

Here is the steps to reproduce the problem:
ip netns add foo
ip netns add bar
ip -n foo link add xfrmi0 type xfrm dev lo if_id 42
ip -n foo link set xfrmi0 netns bar
ip netns del foo
ip netns del bar

Which results to:
